                              margins (rubricated on fols. 15va, 17rb, 23rb, 38rb, 42va, 46ra, 47va,
                              48va, 48vb) indicate the readings for Text I: ዘእሁድ: <locus target="#6vb">fol. 6vb</locus> ዘሚካኤል: <locus target="#11vb">fol.
